      <scopecontent id="aspace_77d1f6c7cc39e2facd2ee04703785c19">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes, sermons, a visitors register, and bulletins documenting the activities of the Church of Christ in Yale University. Also included are the records of Charles Krigbaum, university organist and choir director.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
